@startuml

actor Student
actor Instructor
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Assignment Service" as AssignmentSvc
participant "File Storage Service" as Storage
database "Relational Database" as DB
participant "Email & Notification\nService" as Notify

' Login & Navigation Phase
== Login & Navigation ==
Student -> UI: Enter Credentials
activate UI
UI -> API: POST /auth/login
activate API
API -> DB: Verify user credentials
activate DB
DB --> API: User record + role
deactivate DB
API --> UI: 200 OK + Auth Token
deactivate API
Student -> UI: Navigate to Course Dashboard
UI -> API: GET /courses/{courseId}/assignments
activate API
API -> AssignmentSvc: getAssignments(courseId, studentId)
activate AssignmentSvc
AssignmentSvc -> DB: Query assignments by course
activate DB
DB --> AssignmentSvc: Assignment records
deactivate DB
AssignmentSvc --> API: Assignment list
deactivate AssignmentSvc
API --> UI: Display assignments
deactivate API
Student -> UI: Select assignment & review details and requirements
deactivate UI

' Deadline Check Phase
== Deadline Check ==
UI -> API: GET /assignments/{assignmentId}/deadline
activate UI
activate API
API -> AssignmentSvc: checkDeadline(assignmentId, currentTime)
activate AssignmentSvc
AssignmentSvc -> DB: Query deadline & late submission policy
activate DB
DB --> AssignmentSvc: Deadline timestamp + lateAllowed flag
deactivate DB
alt Past deadline & late submissions allowed
    AssignmentSvc --> API: lateFlag = true
    deactivate AssignmentSvc
    API --> UI: 200 OK — Warn: submission will be flagged as late
    deactivate API
    deactivate UI
else Past deadline & late submissions not allowed
    AssignmentSvc --> API: closed = true
    deactivate AssignmentSvc
    API --> UI: 403 Submission Closed
    deactivate API
    UI --> Student: Display "Submission Closed" message
    deactivate UI
end

' File Upload & Validation Phase
== File Upload & Validation ==
Student -> UI: Attach file (PDF / ZIP / Link)
activate UI
UI -> API: POST /assignments/{assignmentId}/submit (multipart/form-data)
activate API
API -> AssignmentSvc: validateFile(fileType, fileSize, assignmentId)
activate AssignmentSvc
AssignmentSvc -> DB: Fetch allowed file types & size limits
activate DB
DB --> AssignmentSvc: Validation rules
deactivate DB
alt File invalid (type or size)
    AssignmentSvc --> API: 422 Unprocessable Entity — validation error
    deactivate AssignmentSvc
    API --> UI: Display validation error message
    deactivate API
    UI --> Student: Fix & re-upload file
    Student -> UI: Re-attach corrected file
    UI -> API: POST /assignments/{assignmentId}/submit (multipart/form-data)
    activate API
    API -> AssignmentSvc: validateFile(fileType, fileSize, assignmentId)
    activate AssignmentSvc
    AssignmentSvc --> API: 200 OK — file valid
    deactivate AssignmentSvc
end

' Storage Phase
== File Storage ==
API -> Storage: uploadFile(fileData, studentId, assignmentId)
activate Storage
alt Storage failure
    Storage --> API: 500 Upload Failed
    deactivate Storage
    API --> UI: Display upload failure error
    deactivate API
    UI --> Student: Prompted to retry
    deactivate UI
else Storage successful
    Storage --> API: 200 OK + fileUrl
    deactivate Storage
end

' Record & Confirm Phase
== Record & Confirm ==
API -> AssignmentSvc: recordSubmission(studentId, assignmentId, fileUrl, timestamp, lateFlag)
activate AssignmentSvc
AssignmentSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO submissions (studentId, assignmentId, fileUrl, submittedAt, lateFlag)
activate DB
DB --> AssignmentSvc: submissionId
deactivate DB
AssignmentSvc -> DB: UPDATE submissions SET status = "Submitted" WHERE submissionId = {id}
activate DB
DB --> AssignmentSvc: OK
deactivate DB
AssignmentSvc --> API: 201 Created — submissionId confirmed
deactivate AssignmentSvc
API --> UI: 201 Submission Confirmed
deactivate API
UI --> Student: View submission status on dashboard
deactivate UI

' Notification Phase
== Notification ==
API -> Notify: sendReceipt(studentId, submissionId, timestamp)
activate Notify
API -> Notify: notifyInstructor(instructorId, courseId, submissionId)
Notify --> Student: Confirmation email (receipt + submission details)
Notify --> Instructor: New submission notification — queued for grading
deactivate Notify

@enduml
